cz-reprepro (4) unstable; urgency=medium

  * Improve the support for repositories hosted in AFS in
    ca-reprepro-upload.
  * Correct man page generation.
  * Make sure configuration file usage in cz-reprepro-upload and
    reprepro-backend is consistent.
  * Bug fix in reprepro-backup parsing the configuration file.
  * Update reprepro-backend to use --gnupghome switch instead of
    the GNUPGHOME environment variable.
  * Add reprepro-backend-ka wrapper script for repositories that are
    hosted in AFS.

 -- Bill MacAllister <bill@ca-zephyr.org>  Mon, 25 Sep 2023 19:08:09 +0000

